sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant B as Browser<br/>(dadocar1.vercel.app)
  participant V as Vercel proxy<br/>(api/vehicle/plate/[plate].js)
  participant F as Function App<br/>(dadocar-dev-func-enrich-brs)
  participant K as Key Vault<br/>(dadocardevkvbrso3uo)
  participant I as Infocar<br/>(api.datacast3.com)

  Note over B,F: Closed-beta authentication chain
  B->>V: POST /api/vehicle/plate/{plate}<br/>Authorization: Bearer DADOCAR_GATE_SECRET
  V->>F: GET /api/vehicle/plate/{plate}<br/>x-functions-key: AZURE_FUNCTION_KEY
  F->>K: GET secret infocar-id-key<br/>(MI via DefaultAzureCredential)
  K-->>F: secret value
  F->>K: GET secret infocar-username
  K-->>F: secret value
  F->>K: GET secret infocar-password
  K-->>F: secret value
  Note over F,K: KV reads cached ~5 min<br/>(subsequent calls skip K)

  F->>I: POST /api/Token/GerarToken<br/>JSON: credentials
  I-->>F: bearer token (TTL ~8h)
  Note over F,I: Token cached in-process ~7h45m<br/>(subsequent calls skip token round-trip)

  F->>I: GET /api/v1.0/CodificacaoFipe/placa/{plate}<br/>Authorization: Bearer
  I-->>F: vehicle + FIPE payload
  F-->>V: {query, generated_at, ran_providers, sources:[{id,ok,data,latency_ms}]}
  V-->>B: JSON body (verbatim)

  Note over B,I: This is the ENRICHMENT leg (Infocar / FIPE). There are two more legs<br/>with the same shape, consumed by the Placas360 webclient:<br/>• pricing fn dadocar-dev-func-pricing-brs → Molicar / KBB<br/>• checktudo fn dadocar-dev-func-checktudo-brs → CheckTudo<br/>Each function owns one vendor + its own KV secrets + token cache.
